y small and     some of which are heavyweight.</font></li>  <li> Documentation. <A HREF="">Framemaker.</A>.</li></UL><H1>Academic Dishonesty</H1>Cheating in ICS 228 will be dealt with in accordance with <a href="http://www.senate.uci.edu/9_IrvineManual/3ASMAppendices/Appendix08.html">University policy</a> and <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Eucounsel/continuing_students/cheat.html"> ICS policy. </a><A HREF="http://www.reg.uci.edu/REGISTRAR/SOC/adh.html"> </A>Please familiarize yourself with those documents.&nbsp; <HR><ADDRESS><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/">Department of Information and ComputerScience</A>,</ADDRESS><BR>University of California, Irvine CA 92697-3425</BODY></HTML>